%% Diagram: Io Dual Strategy
%% Type: flowchart
graph TD
    App["Application Code"] --> IOType{"I/O Type?"}

    IOType -->|"Network I/O<br/>(TCP, UDP)"| NB["Non-blocking Sockets"]
    NB --> Poll["Kernel Polling<br/>epoll / kqueue / IOCP"]
    Poll --> ELT1["Callback on<br/>Event Loop Thread"]

    IOType -->|"File I/O, DNS"| WQ["Work Queue"]
    WQ --> TP["Thread Pool<br/>Default: 4 workers, max 1024"]
    TP --> Block["Blocking syscall<br/>on worker thread"]
    Block --> ELT2["Callback on<br/>Event Loop Thread"]
